WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.360 --> 00:43.580
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.410 --> 02:50.000
[Episode 32]

02:52.590 --> 02:54.710
She actually broke out of my sea of consciousness.

02:54.740 --> 02:55.790
Impossible!

02:57.540 --> 02:59.920
You're of the Divine Race, but so what?

03:00.410 --> 03:01.740
Didn't you still

03:01.770 --> 03:04.180
lose to my disciple?

03:04.360 --> 03:06.170
You're dead!

03:18.110 --> 03:19.680
Master, are you alright?

03:19.920 --> 03:21.920
I'm good.

03:22.079 --> 03:23.290
I knew there was nothing

03:23.320 --> 03:25.620
that could trap you.

03:25.720 --> 03:27.400
Since you're all here,

03:27.420 --> 03:29.490
none of you are leaving!

03:30.940 --> 03:31.570
Chong Zhao,

03:31.600 --> 03:33.220
take Master and Fu Ling away first.

03:37.780 --> 03:38.860
Be careful!

03:46.860 --> 03:47.700
Let's go!

04:02.360 --> 04:04.330
How did you break out of the sea of consciousness?

04:04.360 --> 04:06.080
I have to thank you for the reminder.

04:06.270 --> 04:07.800
A seal created by divine power

04:07.820 --> 04:09.420
can only be broken by divine power.

04:09.480 --> 04:10.640
Don't forget,

04:10.780 --> 04:12.210
I have the Contemplation Stone in me.

04:12.420 --> 04:14.820
With your power, you could have easily killed me.

04:14.850 --> 04:16.890
Why did you choose to trap me in the sea of consciousness instead

04:16.910 --> 04:18.829
and trick Chong Zhao into killing me?

04:19.370 --> 04:20.610
I told you,

04:21.149 --> 04:22.950
as long as you gave up Bai Shuo,

04:22.970 --> 04:25.080
I'd tell you where the last Contemplation is.

04:25.160 --> 04:26.680
Then you wouldn't have to die,

04:26.680 --> 04:28.510
and we could be together forever.

04:28.540 --> 04:30.380
Why did you still choose her?

04:30.750 --> 04:31.720
Jing Yuan,

04:32.130 --> 04:34.370
I once stayed by your side day and night.

04:35.950 --> 04:37.560
Have you truly forgotten everything?

04:37.580 --> 04:38.850
I'm not Jing Yuan.

04:39.370 --> 04:41.210
I don't care who you are either.

04:41.420 --> 04:42.310
To me,

04:42.310 --> 04:44.530
you've committed too many sins,

04:44.770 --> 04:46.040
and you deserve death.

04:46.690 --> 04:48.740
I deserve death?

04:49.720 --> 04:51.840
I've waited for you for 60,000 years

04:53.140 --> 04:55.659
only to hear this?

04:55.980 --> 04:57.990
You say you're not Jing Yuan,

04:58.270 --> 04:59.390
but what you've always loved

04:59.409 --> 05:01.460
is just Xing Yue's outward appearance!

05:01.490 --> 05:02.650
You've been bewitched by her,

05:02.670 --> 05:04.630
unable to distinguish true love from fake feelings.

05:04.650 --> 05:06.500
You really think you have true love

05:06.530 --> 05:07.650
that will last forever?

05:07.670 --> 05:08.790
What a joke!

05:08.820 --> 05:11.550
The world reveres, worships, and admires her.

05:11.570 --> 05:12.960
But do you know

05:12.990 --> 05:14.990
Xing Yue's everlasting reputation

05:15.010 --> 05:16.420
was built, bit by bit,

05:16.450 --> 05:18.290
on your dead body?

05:19.950 --> 05:21.010
What do you mean?

05:21.040 --> 05:22.160
Bai Shuo once asked me

05:22.190 --> 05:24.160
why I have so much hostility toward her.

05:24.180 --> 05:25.740
I'll tell you now.

05:25.760 --> 05:28.230
Because during the Divine War 60,000 years ago,

05:28.250 --> 05:30.020
it was Xing Yue who killed you.

05:30.050 --> 05:31.350
And Bai Shuo

05:31.950 --> 05:34.100
carries Xing Yue's Divine Mantle!

05:48.080 --> 05:49.540
The past is the past.

05:50.130 --> 05:52.000
The grudges and entanglements from 60,000 years ago

05:52.360 --> 05:54.520
were between Jing Yuan and Xing Yue.

05:55.120 --> 05:56.630
They have nothing to do with me!

05:57.550 --> 05:58.790
You are not him

06:00.240 --> 06:01.680
after all.

06:03.250 --> 06:05.340
Since you're heartless,

06:05.800 --> 06:07.720
I don't have to hold back anymore.

07:00.300 --> 07:01.560
The divine power of those puppets

07:01.560 --> 07:02.850
has all been absorbed back into her body.

07:02.880 --> 07:04.770
Since you love each other so much,

07:04.790 --> 07:06.350
I'll grant your wish

07:06.380 --> 07:08.410
and let you live and die together!

07:44.950 --> 07:46.300
Reclaiming the divine power is her backup plan.

07:46.320 --> 07:47.320
We have one too.

07:47.350 --> 07:48.210
Do you remember?

07:48.230 --> 07:50.830
My blood can make demons stronger.

08:49.500 --> 08:51.050
The tides of the Lunar Hidden Sea have ebbed and flowed for tens of thousands of years,

08:51.080 --> 08:52.430
creating some crystals.

08:52.780 --> 08:54.800
I found them interesting and collected them.

08:54.960 --> 08:56.850
You don't like jewelry,

08:57.090 --> 08:58.370
but this is made of stone.

08:58.760 --> 09:00.490
Lunar Lord, you won't refuse it, will you?

09:07.500 --> 09:10.180
In scattered flowers and flying petals,

09:11.470 --> 09:14.790
my once youthful face has changed.

09:15.990 --> 09:18.720
It turns out that

09:18.970 --> 09:20.210
what is truly eternal

09:21.600 --> 09:24.290
has never been you and me.

10:02.710 --> 10:03.660
My master.

10:20.400 --> 10:24.010
Lanling isn't a place you can come and go as you please.

10:26.790 --> 10:28.190
But, Sect Leader,

10:28.220 --> 10:30.100
didn't you still let me in?

10:33.160 --> 10:35.540
If you come uninvited again,

10:35.760 --> 10:37.810
I'll have to deal with you according to the laws of Lanling.

10:37.840 --> 10:39.030
The laws?

10:40.510 --> 10:43.080
Will Lanling still need laws in the future?

10:43.100 --> 10:44.490
Won't you, Sect Leader,

10:44.660 --> 10:46.580
be the law of Lanling?

10:48.930 --> 10:51.520
I've been killing demons according to the map you gave me,

10:51.550 --> 10:52.960
and I've given all the demon cores to you.

10:52.980 --> 10:54.290
What else do you want?

10:56.430 --> 10:57.510
Here,

10:57.530 --> 11:00.020
a new map of the demon clans.

11:01.300 --> 11:03.420
I need more demon cores

11:03.440 --> 11:04.930
to restore my vitality.

11:05.730 --> 11:06.820
I hope

11:07.120 --> 11:08.830
you can keep up the good work.

11:08.850 --> 11:11.560
This battle was won too easily.

11:11.630 --> 11:14.160
If things continue to go so smoothly,

11:14.220 --> 11:16.290
it'll surely arouse suspicion among other High Eternals.

11:16.360 --> 11:17.570
If anyone suspects anything,

11:17.590 --> 11:18.860
just send them

11:18.920 --> 11:20.560
to Bodhi Village

11:20.580 --> 11:21.720
and be done with it.

11:22.230 --> 11:23.590
Don't worry, Sect Leader.

11:23.620 --> 11:24.740
In the demon-slaying battles,

11:24.760 --> 11:26.380
the fame and glory

11:26.550 --> 11:27.630
will all be yours.

11:27.650 --> 11:28.740
You'll become

11:28.770 --> 11:31.300
the undisputed head

11:31.330 --> 11:33.250
of the Eternals.

11:44.420 --> 11:46.480
Why is there suddenly a disturbance in my spiritual power?

11:46.840 --> 11:47.670
Has something

11:47.690 --> 11:49.080
happened to Luan Zhu?

12:03.150 --> 12:04.280
No!

12:04.510 --> 12:06.540
The power of Eternals and demons is incompatible.

12:06.740 --> 12:08.500
Both Fan Yue and I are demons,

12:08.530 --> 12:10.180
and you also carry demonic power within you.

12:10.200 --> 12:12.270
Right now, only Bai Shuo can help him.

12:21.240 --> 12:22.170
Master.

12:22.730 --> 12:23.940
You're finally awake.

12:34.210 --> 12:36.570
I've lived for over 1,000 years.

12:36.600 --> 12:38.430
I've experienced everything.

12:38.450 --> 12:39.850
I won't die.

12:40.730 --> 12:41.700
Master,

12:42.390 --> 12:43.840
how did you end up in Bodhi Village?

12:45.160 --> 12:46.130
It was Jin Yao.

12:46.720 --> 12:48.600
I accidentally discovered that he's

12:48.620 --> 12:51.330
secretly adopted ancient mental cultivation methods.

12:51.440 --> 12:53.970
So, he captured me and brought me to Bodhi Village

12:54.000 --> 12:55.530
as an offering to Luan Zhu.

12:55.850 --> 12:57.790
The corpses in that cave

12:57.860 --> 13:00.220
were all Eternals sent here by Jin Yao.

13:00.250 --> 13:02.770
Every time Luan Zhu drains an Eternal,

13:02.790 --> 13:04.120
she creates a puppet

13:04.150 --> 13:06.060
identical to them.

13:08.360 --> 13:09.600
All of this

13:10.690 --> 13:12.770
was actually done by Sect Leader.

13:14.460 --> 13:15.710
Then what about my parents?

13:16.090 --> 13:17.970
Did my parents really die in Bodhi Village?

13:18.680 --> 13:19.580
Well...

13:19.610 --> 13:20.860
I don't know.

13:20.880 --> 13:22.940
At least, their remains were not in the cave.

13:22.970 --> 13:24.690
Luan Zhu has drained countless Eternals

13:24.710 --> 13:26.680
over the centuries.

13:26.730 --> 13:27.890
Perhaps

13:27.990 --> 13:29.930
they've been hidden somewhere else.

13:43.990 --> 13:45.440
There's something

13:46.010 --> 13:49.050
I've been keeping inside for a very long time.

13:49.130 --> 13:50.890
Now that everyone is here,

13:51.860 --> 13:54.320
it's time for me to face it.

13:56.240 --> 13:57.310
You've always

13:57.930 --> 13:59.080
wanted to know

13:59.080 --> 14:01.720
why I've been hiding in Lanling, haven't you?

14:02.090 --> 14:03.760
I've been hiding from someone—

14:04.490 --> 14:05.390
Zhen Yu.

14:06.680 --> 14:07.680
Zhen Yu?

14:08.390 --> 14:10.580
Zhen Yu has been searching for

14:10.610 --> 14:12.900
three children with special fates.

14:14.030 --> 14:16.860
10 years ago, he captured me

14:17.220 --> 14:20.530
and forced me to find those three children by divination.

14:21.170 --> 14:22.520
To stay alive,

14:22.540 --> 14:24.780
I told him about two of them.

14:25.920 --> 14:27.210
One was

14:27.230 --> 14:28.420
in the Bai family

14:28.450 --> 14:29.550
in Ning'an City,

14:29.640 --> 14:30.880
and the other was

14:31.880 --> 14:33.050
in the Bai Ze Clan.

14:36.590 --> 14:38.260
So it was you

14:39.180 --> 14:40.580
who brought Zhen Yu there.

14:47.250 --> 14:49.460
I know I'm deeply sinful.

14:49.490 --> 14:51.250
I've wronged the Bai family,

14:51.270 --> 14:53.210
and I've wronged the Bai Ze Clan.

14:54.790 --> 14:57.420
I've been racked with guilt.

14:57.440 --> 14:58.800
But the guiltier I felt,

14:58.830 --> 15:02.170
the harder it was to tell you the truth.

15:05.840 --> 15:07.600
When Zhen Yu forced you to do the reading,

15:08.610 --> 15:10.560
did you know what would happen afterward?

15:11.130 --> 15:12.520
If I had known

15:12.970 --> 15:14.400
that my divination

15:14.430 --> 15:18.880
would bring so much bloodshed and suffering,

15:19.490 --> 15:23.280
I would never have done it, even if it cost me my life.

15:23.450 --> 15:26.050
But there are no "ifs" in this world.

15:26.080 --> 15:27.790
What's done is done.

15:27.810 --> 15:29.690
What's wrong is wrong.

15:30.180 --> 15:32.300
It's all my fault.

15:33.090 --> 15:33.930
Did you tell Zhen Yu

15:33.960 --> 15:35.580
the whereabouts of the third child?

15:35.610 --> 15:37.370
I didn't know why Zhen Yu was searching for

15:37.390 --> 15:38.750
those three children,

15:38.780 --> 15:40.690
but fearing he might succeed in his schemes,

15:40.720 --> 15:42.270
I didn't continue the divination.

15:42.290 --> 15:44.570
I lied to him and said that

15:45.200 --> 15:46.670
the third child hadn't been born yet.

15:47.090 --> 15:48.140
Zhen Yu,

15:49.220 --> 15:51.040
the culprit.

15:51.460 --> 15:52.790
It's him again.

15:58.250 --> 15:59.200
Master.

15:59.330 --> 16:00.220
How did this happen?

16:00.250 --> 16:01.410
Weren't you just fine?

16:01.430 --> 16:02.670
I'll give more spiritual power to you.

16:02.700 --> 16:04.610
No, it's useless.

16:04.630 --> 16:06.270
Luan Zhu injured my very foundation.

16:06.300 --> 16:07.870
There's no saving me.

16:17.170 --> 16:18.130
Take this.

16:18.390 --> 16:19.560
It's my...

16:19.600 --> 16:21.170
my turtle shell.

16:21.200 --> 16:22.560
Why are you giving this to me?

16:23.000 --> 16:23.550
I don't want it.

16:23.570 --> 16:25.530
I said take it, so take it!

16:25.560 --> 16:27.600
You keep your own turtle shell!

16:27.620 --> 16:29.580
This is the shell of a 1000-year-old Mystery Turtle.

16:29.630 --> 16:30.480
Use it in medicine.

16:30.480 --> 16:33.480
It might help you make the first-grade elixir.

16:33.630 --> 16:34.700
Take it

16:34.960 --> 16:37.160
and save the person you want to save.

16:37.180 --> 16:39.140
Consider it a small act

16:39.810 --> 16:41.340
of atonement from me.

16:46.050 --> 16:47.090
Master.

16:48.170 --> 16:50.340
I want you to live.

16:50.870 --> 16:53.120
I don't allow you to die.

16:53.560 --> 16:56.590
You're still willing to call me "Master."

16:56.620 --> 16:58.070
Then even in death,

16:58.090 --> 16:59.380
I'll have no regrets.

17:02.240 --> 17:03.210
Do you remember,

17:03.230 --> 17:05.960
when you were training with me in Lanling,

17:06.569 --> 17:10.369
what I told you life was about?

17:11.770 --> 17:14.119
Life is the journey

17:14.150 --> 17:15.710
from having nothing

17:15.730 --> 17:18.160
back to having nothing.

17:18.190 --> 17:19.619
In growing up,

17:19.680 --> 17:21.640
you must learn to accept gains and losses.

17:23.579 --> 17:25.710
I've always loved freedom.

17:25.740 --> 17:26.819
Now,

17:27.380 --> 17:29.860
I'm finally free.

17:36.700 --> 17:41.010
♫The flowers flew away♫

17:44.170 --> 17:48.340
♫My tears are streaming down like rain♫

17:51.530 --> 17:52.400
Master.

17:52.750 --> 18:00.090
♫Light my heart's lamp, cast away attachments, and ask the world♫

17:57.160 --> 17:58.230
Master!

18:00.850 --> 18:06.850
♫On the vast sea, you and I♫

18:02.550 --> 18:04.160
Master!

18:07.250 --> 18:08.960
Master!

18:27.720 --> 18:29.660
Let me borrow your turtle shell for a bit.

18:30.010 --> 18:31.590
The shell of a 1000-year-old Mystery Turtle

18:31.610 --> 18:32.630
can make divination more accurate.

18:32.780 --> 18:34.500
After I die,

18:34.530 --> 18:36.160
my shell

18:36.180 --> 18:37.960
will be yours.

18:38.570 --> 18:40.290
And when will that be?

18:40.390 --> 18:42.460
Are you that eager for me to die?

18:43.690 --> 18:44.930
Of course not!

18:44.960 --> 18:46.610
I just think that a turtle like you

18:46.630 --> 18:47.950
will probably live longer than me.

18:48.000 --> 18:49.920
I can't really count on getting your shell.

18:50.270 --> 18:51.770
Good that you know.

19:08.460 --> 19:10.980
In the end, I still couldn't save Master.

19:11.470 --> 19:12.910
You did your best.

19:13.660 --> 19:15.440
I used to think

19:16.470 --> 19:18.760
since Master was a Mystery Turtle of the Eternal Race,

19:19.140 --> 19:21.310
he would live for a very, very long time.

19:22.790 --> 19:24.640
I never thought he would leave me,

19:26.250 --> 19:28.290
let alone so suddenly.

19:33.890 --> 19:35.550
I used to pester him,

19:36.120 --> 19:37.430
bicker with him,

19:38.250 --> 19:39.820
and even steal his wine.

19:41.990 --> 19:43.670
Back then, I thought

19:44.190 --> 19:45.560
there was plenty of time ahead,

19:46.810 --> 19:49.020
and I could make it up to him later.

19:50.350 --> 19:52.720
But when the unexpected happened,

19:53.120 --> 19:54.890
I realized that the "plenty of time" I counted on

19:55.950 --> 19:57.150
was never real.

20:05.120 --> 20:07.200
So do whatever you want to do.

20:08.250 --> 20:09.160
Don't wait.

20:21.690 --> 20:23.160
Although Luan Zhu is dead,

20:23.880 --> 20:26.270
many unanswered mysteries remain.

20:26.400 --> 20:28.440
My parents' bodies still haven't been found.

20:28.470 --> 20:30.730
You'll have to stay here a bit longer.

20:30.760 --> 20:32.300
They're your parents,

20:32.320 --> 20:34.140
trapped here by Luan Zhu for 10 years.

20:34.170 --> 20:36.020
Of course, you must find them.

20:36.430 --> 20:37.720
I'll be

20:37.740 --> 20:38.850
wherever you are.

20:43.120 --> 20:45.770
Shuo used to love looking at the starry sky.

20:45.790 --> 20:47.380
I often looked at it with her.

20:50.340 --> 20:52.070
You're so close to her now.

20:54.330 --> 20:55.440
Unfortunately,

20:55.470 --> 20:56.920
we can't go back to the past.

20:59.360 --> 21:00.990
No matter what has happened,

21:01.010 --> 21:02.300
you are still Bai Xi.

21:10.490 --> 21:12.200
You have to face what you should.

21:13.410 --> 21:15.020
Don't leave yourself with regrets.

21:38.510 --> 21:40.380
Mother used to say

21:41.210 --> 21:42.730
after people die,

21:43.750 --> 21:45.790
they become stars in the sky.

21:46.970 --> 21:48.340
After Father and Mother passed away,

21:49.160 --> 21:51.360
I often looked up at the stars,

21:52.230 --> 21:53.950
trying to find where they were.

21:55.570 --> 21:58.720
But I never looked for Xi's star

21:57.960 --> 22:01.350
♫Don't linger, don't regret♫

22:01.750 --> 22:03.920
because I always believed

22:02.380 --> 22:04.740
♫The last moonlight♫

22:05.360 --> 22:06.710
she wasn't dead.

22:05.770 --> 22:09.390
♫The water from my hometown flows gently♫

22:10.560 --> 22:13.190
♫Sending me to the distant place♫

22:13.880 --> 22:17.890
♫In this life, at this time♫

22:13.930 --> 22:16.120
Stop running away.

22:18.230 --> 22:21.600
♫I dare not look back♫

22:18.990 --> 22:20.710
When we were little,

22:21.080 --> 22:23.160
you always stood in front of me to protect me.

22:22.480 --> 22:25.700
♫Is there the same moonlight♫

22:23.720 --> 22:25.620
I thought my sister was the bravest person

22:25.680 --> 22:28.030
in the world, second only to Father.

22:26.750 --> 22:29.930
♫On your path?♫

22:29.560 --> 22:30.440
But why doesn't she

22:30.440 --> 22:32.240
even have the courage to face me now?

22:30.760 --> 22:33.800
♫I'm walking on a never-ending long road♫

22:34.330 --> 22:37.470
♫In the vast world, how can I get there?♫

22:38.450 --> 22:40.310
♫In the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped♫

22:39.050 --> 22:41.150
It's my fault that he died.

22:40.960 --> 22:41.940
♫The moonlight is gentle♫

22:42.560 --> 22:45.390
♫All the feelings turned into nothing but a dream♫

22:43.740 --> 22:46.700
My hands are covered with blood, and I've done all the bad things.

22:46.730 --> 22:48.550
I'm not worthy to be your sister.

22:46.810 --> 22:49.900
♫Reminiscing about the good old days♫

22:50.330 --> 22:53.450
♫Singing until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost♫

22:51.050 --> 22:52.590
I'm even less so…

22:54.280 --> 22:56.310
♫Forget all about the past and leave it behind♫

22:55.190 --> 22:57.160
to be his daughter.

22:56.990 --> 22:58.460
♫Time after time♫

22:58.080 --> 22:59.600
If Father were still here,

22:59.330 --> 23:04.050
♫Oh, melancholy♫

23:01.310 --> 23:03.660
he'd just be happy that you're alive,

23:03.680 --> 23:05.090
that you're safe and sound.

23:06.610 --> 23:08.310
He would never blame you.

23:11.340 --> 23:14.290
♫Don't linger, don't regret♫

23:15.590 --> 23:17.930
♫The last moonlight♫

23:16.050 --> 23:17.550
I promised Father

23:19.000 --> 23:22.400
♫The water from my hometown flows gently♫

23:19.190 --> 23:20.540
that I'd find you.

23:22.190 --> 23:23.200
Xi.

23:23.540 --> 23:25.340
I've grown up.

23:23.680 --> 23:26.210
♫Sending me to the distant place♫

23:26.560 --> 23:28.420
I can protect you now.

23:27.170 --> 23:30.960
♫In this life, at this time♫

23:29.260 --> 23:31.270
Let me take you back and cure the poison.

23:31.530 --> 23:33.090
Come home with me,

23:31.610 --> 23:34.830
♫I dare not look back♫

23:33.110 --> 23:34.100
okay?

23:35.740 --> 23:38.810
♫Is there the same moonlight♫

23:38.480 --> 23:40.030
Outside Ning'an City,

23:40.060 --> 23:42.160
the hibiscus flowers you loved

23:40.140 --> 23:43.030
♫On your path?♫

23:42.310 --> 23:44.130
have bloomed season after season.

23:43.920 --> 23:46.890
♫I'm walking on a never-ending long road♫

23:44.270 --> 23:45.900
In the Governor's Mansion,

23:45.930 --> 23:48.430
the cherry tree you planted

23:47.350 --> 23:50.850
♫In the vast world, how can I get there?♫

23:48.450 --> 23:51.200
has grown its rings year after year.

23:51.530 --> 23:52.980
♫In the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped♫

23:53.270 --> 23:54.750
It's been 10 years.

23:53.920 --> 23:55.230
♫The moonlight is gentle♫

23:55.420 --> 23:56.880
It's time for you to come back.

23:55.640 --> 23:58.890
♫All the feelings turned into nothing but a dream♫

23:58.920 --> 23:59.810
Xi,

23:59.600 --> 24:02.990
♫Reminiscing about the good old days♫

23:59.830 --> 24:01.030
it's time to come home.

24:02.620 --> 24:04.140
Let's go home,

24:03.440 --> 24:06.760
♫Singing until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost♫

24:04.160 --> 24:05.260
okay?

24:07.290 --> 24:09.620
♫Forget all about the past and leave it behind♫

24:10.070 --> 24:14.060
♫Time after time♫

24:11.250 --> 24:12.590
Shuo.

24:19.550 --> 24:21.100
Shuo.

24:19.740 --> 24:21.030
♫In the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped♫

24:22.030 --> 24:23.180
♫The moonlight is gentle♫

24:23.680 --> 24:26.770
♫All the feelings turned into nothing but a dream♫

24:27.520 --> 24:30.990
♫Reminiscing about the good old days♫

24:31.570 --> 24:34.800
♫Singing until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost♫

24:35.430 --> 24:37.640
♫Forget all about the past and leave it behind♫

24:38.280 --> 24:39.420
♫Time after time♫

24:40.810 --> 24:47.190
♫Oh, melancholy♫

24:54.550 --> 24:55.910
Mystery Turtle said that Zhen Yu

24:55.930 --> 24:58.010
was looking for three children with special fates.

24:58.030 --> 24:59.310
Now it seems,

24:59.340 --> 25:00.690
one is Fan Yue,

25:00.710 --> 25:01.800
and one is Shuo.

25:02.680 --> 25:04.600
Who is the third child?

25:09.670 --> 25:12.020
Grand Master never mentioned it before.

25:13.040 --> 25:14.280
Why did he

25:14.310 --> 25:15.770
let you go so easily today?

25:15.800 --> 25:17.040
You already went against his order

25:17.060 --> 25:18.920
and saved me from the secret chamber.

25:18.950 --> 25:20.760
Today, you pried into his secret,

25:20.780 --> 25:22.780
yet he just accepted the excuse I made up and let you go.

25:22.810 --> 25:24.610
I think he found something

25:24.630 --> 25:25.840
in me.

25:25.870 --> 25:27.220
And I've also felt

25:27.240 --> 25:28.160
he has something

25:28.190 --> 25:29.470
other than demonic power in him.

25:29.910 --> 25:31.390
Something other than demonic power?

25:34.210 --> 25:36.130
Zhen Yu injected demonic power into my body.

25:36.160 --> 25:38.000
He wants me to completely become a demon!

25:38.020 --> 25:39.830
The magic of Eternals and demons is incompatible.

25:39.860 --> 25:40.580
Doing this

25:40.600 --> 25:42.780
will only damage your foundation and make you die.

25:42.810 --> 25:44.380
What exactly does Grand Master want to do?

25:46.050 --> 25:48.480
Chong Zhao repeatedly defied Zhen Yu,

25:48.860 --> 25:50.830
yet Zhen Yu didn't kill him.

25:50.860 --> 25:52.410
But he injected demonic power into him.

25:52.430 --> 25:53.600
Why was that?

25:55.400 --> 25:56.850
Is Chong Zhao...

25:57.930 --> 25:59.650
No, impossible.

25:59.680 --> 26:01.130
I must be mistaken.

26:14.870 --> 26:16.260
You're sitting here all alone.

26:16.280 --> 26:17.370
What are you thinking about?

26:18.540 --> 26:19.300
Nothing.

26:24.850 --> 26:25.640
What's wrong?

26:27.150 --> 26:27.990
Nothing.

26:29.630 --> 26:30.420
Should we

26:30.860 --> 26:33.640
go look for your parents' remains?

26:34.300 --> 26:35.780
I was about to go.

26:35.810 --> 26:36.750
I'll go with you.

26:37.410 --> 26:38.610
Are you feeling better?

26:39.220 --> 26:41.640
Don't worry. I'm not that fragile.

26:41.660 --> 26:42.290
Let's go.

26:49.630 --> 26:51.030
You haven't fully recovered yet.

26:51.060 --> 26:52.100
Don't catch a cold.

26:56.160 --> 26:57.720
I've imagined countless times

26:57.720 --> 26:59.510
what it would be like to reunite with Xi.

27:00.300 --> 27:01.770
But I never thought

27:01.790 --> 27:03.660
it would happen right after Master's passing.

27:04.420 --> 27:05.890
Life is truly

27:06.240 --> 27:08.200
a mix of joy and sorrow,

27:08.560 --> 27:09.860
full of unexpected changes.

27:10.990 --> 27:12.800
No matter how much the world around you changes,

27:13.260 --> 27:15.370
I'll always stay the same by your side.

27:22.030 --> 27:23.820
To be honest,

27:23.850 --> 27:25.770
I've had suspicions.

27:26.290 --> 27:27.520
About what?

27:27.920 --> 27:30.270
Why did the Contemplation Stone enter my body?

27:30.910 --> 27:33.420
Why am I the only one who can activate it and gather Contemplations?

27:34.280 --> 27:36.270
And why does my blood have miraculous effects?

27:34.720 --> 27:38.210
♫The person standing far away♫

27:37.080 --> 27:39.370
I wondered if I might be special.

27:39.070 --> 27:41.390
♫Don't be afraid♫

27:39.490 --> 27:41.280
Now, I finally have the answer.

27:41.780 --> 27:46.280
♫The stars will guide you to me♫

27:41.960 --> 27:43.830
But the words "Xing Yue's Divine Mantle"

27:44.770 --> 27:46.160
feel both so light

27:46.730 --> 27:48.200
and so heavy.

27:47.280 --> 27:53.730
♫Walk towards me♫

27:49.740 --> 27:51.420
What's worrying you, Shuo?

27:51.990 --> 27:54.300
Xing Yue was a deity who saved the world,

27:54.400 --> 27:56.400
but I'm just an ordinary human.

27:55.470 --> 27:58.390
♫My heart feels so...♫

27:57.160 --> 27:58.240
I don't know

27:58.240 --> 27:59.960
what this Divine Mantle truly means.

27:58.850 --> 28:04.790
♫It's pounding as I wait for you♫

28:00.350 --> 28:01.490
And

28:01.610 --> 28:04.060
the story between Xing Yue and Jing Yuan

28:04.400 --> 28:05.840
doesn't seem to have a happy ending.

28:06.270 --> 28:08.510
You mean the part where Xing Yue killed Jing Yuan?

28:06.670 --> 28:10.410
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

28:09.930 --> 28:12.090
Don't take what Luan Zhu said to heart.

28:12.530 --> 28:14.330
It's not because of what Luan Zhu said.

28:14.170 --> 28:17.510
♫You are my distant call♫

28:14.360 --> 28:15.840
I saw it.

28:16.510 --> 28:18.180
When I was in the sea of consciousness,

28:18.000 --> 28:22.380
♫You are my first and last♫

28:18.210 --> 28:20.150
some images flashed through my mind.

28:20.400 --> 28:22.310
Xing Yue and Jing Yuan

28:22.650 --> 28:24.740
weren't just lovers.

28:23.200 --> 28:29.290
♫My heart is trembling for you♫

28:25.350 --> 28:27.520
Unfortunately, I couldn't see more.

28:29.710 --> 28:32.560
♫In this moment where we embrace each other♫

28:32.000 --> 28:34.490
That's all in the past.

28:33.360 --> 28:37.460
♫Let's never let go♫

28:34.530 --> 28:36.840
This time, we've met again,

28:36.870 --> 28:38.460
not as Xing Yue and Jing Yuan,

28:38.940 --> 28:40.390
but as Bai Shuo and Fan Yue.

28:41.860 --> 28:42.820
To me,

28:43.200 --> 28:44.810
you're the best Bai Shuo,

28:45.530 --> 28:47.250
the only one in this world,

28:47.600 --> 28:48.840
irreplaceable.

28:54.320 --> 28:55.730
There's one more thing.

28:55.750 --> 28:57.580
The Contemplation Stone showed a prophetic vision,

28:57.760 --> 29:00.050
which means the fifth Contemplation is in Bodhi Village.

29:00.070 --> 29:01.420
Now that Luan Zhu is dead

29:01.460 --> 29:03.220
and the villagers are gone,

29:03.250 --> 29:05.090
it seems like everything has settled.

29:05.120 --> 29:06.900
But why hasn't the fifth Contemplation appeared yet?

29:07.340 --> 29:08.420
Let's just let it play out.

29:09.590 --> 29:10.700
What's meant to happen will happen.

29:20.230 --> 29:21.390
I didn't find anything.

29:21.410 --> 29:22.490
Neither did I.

29:22.520 --> 29:25.280
Mystery Turtle said the bodies in the cave weren't all of them,

29:25.300 --> 29:27.440
but we've searched the entire village and found nothing.

29:27.470 --> 29:28.580
Could it be

29:28.600 --> 29:30.410
Luan Zhu destroyed them to cover her tracks?

29:31.200 --> 29:32.770
Luan Zhu cooperated with Jin Yao,

29:32.800 --> 29:34.200
but it was purely for mutual benefit.

29:34.270 --> 29:35.870
They must have had their own agendas.

29:35.900 --> 29:36.730
Luan Zhu must have

29:36.750 --> 29:38.270
kept something as leverage over Jin Yao,

29:38.570 --> 29:39.610
and it might be related

29:39.630 --> 29:40.920
to the Eternals who were killed.

29:41.250 --> 29:42.200
You have a point.

29:42.230 --> 29:43.120
In that case,

29:43.140 --> 29:44.380
let's go search Luan Zhu's room.

29:44.410 --> 29:45.680
There might be new clues.

30:36.510 --> 30:37.270
Chong Zhao.

30:56.430 --> 30:57.470
These

30:57.820 --> 30:59.690
are tokens carried by Eternal disciples

30:59.720 --> 31:01.200
as a form of identification.

31:04.560 --> 31:08.870
[Chen Xuan] [Pei Yue]

31:16.110 --> 31:17.430
[Meng Ning]

31:19.610 --> 31:21.170
[Meng Ning] [Chong Tai]

31:25.540 --> 31:26.330
Father.

31:27.000 --> 31:29.110
[Meng Ning] [Chong Tai]

31:27.690 --> 31:28.490
Mother.

31:31.740 --> 31:33.750
The truth you've been looking for for 10 years

31:34.150 --> 31:35.250
has finally

31:35.450 --> 31:37.040
been uncovered today.

31:38.020 --> 31:39.770
[Meng Ning] [Chong Tai]

31:41.160 --> 31:42.920
Each of these tokens

31:43.130 --> 31:45.340
represents a fallen Eternal.

31:45.370 --> 31:46.380
These

31:46.400 --> 31:48.750
are the evidence of Luan Zhu and Jin Yao's crimes.

31:48.770 --> 31:51.370
My four uncles must still be kept in the dark by Jin Yao.

31:51.950 --> 31:52.960
I need to return to Lanling

31:52.980 --> 31:54.570
and tell them everything.

31:55.060 --> 31:56.120
I'll go with you.

31:56.900 --> 31:58.380
The poison in you hasn't been cured yet,

31:58.410 --> 31:59.140
and they don't know

31:59.160 --> 32:00.940
you've already left Cold Spring Palace.

32:01.660 --> 32:03.380
You've just reunited with Shuo.

32:03.410 --> 32:05.320
Go back with them to Bright Moon Palace and wait for me there.

32:05.340 --> 32:06.140
But...

32:06.170 --> 32:07.040
Don't worry.

32:07.350 --> 32:08.830
I'm Lanling's head disciple.

32:08.850 --> 32:09.940
They'll believe me.

32:10.260 --> 32:13.640
So Luan Zhu hid the Eternals' tokens here.

32:17.570 --> 32:21.280
I really need to thank you two for helping me find them.

32:41.750 --> 32:43.720
Where did Xi and Chong Zhao go?

32:44.390 --> 32:45.270
They might have gone to look for

32:45.270 --> 32:46.630
the remains of Chong Tai and Meng Ning.

32:46.660 --> 32:47.750
Old Turtle said

32:47.770 --> 32:48.830
that many Eternals' bodies

32:48.830 --> 32:50.170
are still in Bodhi Village.

32:50.200 --> 32:51.780
They're all evidence of Jin Yao's crimes.

32:52.610 --> 32:53.990
Let's go help them.

32:55.370 --> 32:57.380
I'll give these pills to Xi.

32:57.400 --> 32:58.680
Once we're back at Bright Moon Palace,

32:58.710 --> 33:00.380
I can definitely create the antidote.

33:01.450 --> 33:02.300
Let's go.

33:05.170 --> 33:06.090
What?

33:06.110 --> 33:07.560
After just a few days apart,

33:07.590 --> 33:10.150
you don't even want to call me Master anymore?

33:10.180 --> 33:12.710
Did you really send them to Bodhi Village?

33:13.620 --> 33:15.030
Yes.

33:15.060 --> 33:17.260
Every Eternal on this wall

33:17.280 --> 33:20.130
was personally sent here by me.

33:21.840 --> 33:24.210
My parents were your closest friends.

33:24.660 --> 33:26.500
Why did you kill them?

33:29.180 --> 33:32.000
I gave them many chances.

33:32.610 --> 33:34.240
Back then, Chong Tai and Meng Ning

33:34.260 --> 33:35.910
accidentally noticed

33:35.940 --> 33:38.430
the disappearances of some Eternals

33:38.710 --> 33:40.420
and pursued the matter relentlessly.

33:40.450 --> 33:42.440
I tried to stop them multiple times,

33:43.240 --> 33:45.170
but they refused to give up.

33:45.720 --> 33:46.870
Later,

33:46.900 --> 33:49.780
they discovered my secret with Luan Zhu.

33:49.910 --> 33:52.370
I never intended to take their lives,

33:52.620 --> 33:54.750
but they were stubborn

33:54.780 --> 33:56.740
and determined to stand against me.

33:57.480 --> 33:59.590
Standing against me

34:01.870 --> 34:03.920
can only lead to death.

34:05.400 --> 34:07.960
My parents were loyal and kind their entire lives,

34:07.990 --> 34:10.639
devoted to Lanling and caring for the people.

34:10.659 --> 34:13.060
You were their most trusted senior.

34:13.270 --> 34:15.460
How could you bring yourself to do it?

34:18.920 --> 34:21.270
It was indeed difficult,

34:22.150 --> 34:24.540
but your parents didn't know when to quit.

34:25.790 --> 34:27.600
You really can't blame me.

34:30.190 --> 34:31.330
Chong Zhao,

34:31.510 --> 34:34.679
your parents' remains were destroyed back then.

34:35.370 --> 34:36.699
You won't find them.

34:36.730 --> 34:39.600
If you can forget everything that happened in Bodhi Village,

34:39.909 --> 34:41.949
I'll spare your life.

34:41.969 --> 34:43.449
Consider it my way of honoring

34:43.480 --> 34:44.929
our master-disciple bond.

34:47.110 --> 34:50.110
Whatever choice my parents made back then,

34:51.239 --> 34:53.190
I'll make the same one now.

34:54.179 --> 34:55.699
I won't compromise.

35:01.960 --> 35:02.990
Jin Yao,

35:03.710 --> 35:05.750
you conspired with Luan Zhu to kill your own kind.

35:05.780 --> 35:07.870
What right do you have to call yourself Chong Zhao's master?

35:07.900 --> 35:09.500
It's time to show the world

35:09.580 --> 35:11.840
what a hypocrite you are.

35:12.060 --> 35:14.960
There are precedents of humans turning into demons,

35:15.040 --> 35:17.610
but you, when you were a mere human,

35:17.630 --> 35:19.750
survived two of my strikes without dying.

35:20.530 --> 35:23.380
That's something I still don't understand to this day.

35:23.550 --> 35:24.640
Then, today,

35:25.040 --> 35:26.330
take that question with you

35:26.360 --> 35:28.990
and think about it on your way to hell.

35:31.590 --> 35:33.990
You think you two alone can kill me?

35:35.580 --> 35:37.370
What if they have my help?

35:45.400 --> 35:47.000
Since you worked with Luan Zhu,

35:47.110 --> 35:49.360
you should know that I'm here. How dare you still come?

35:52.380 --> 35:54.000
After the fight with Luan Zhu,

35:54.000 --> 35:56.190
you guys are either weakened or injured.

35:56.670 --> 35:59.510
If I don't strike now, when else should I?

36:00.100 --> 36:02.380
You caused my master's death?

36:02.400 --> 36:05.070
Your master was really unlucky.

36:05.100 --> 36:07.180
He discovered the secret between Luan Zhu and me.

36:08.100 --> 36:09.590
He had lived for over 1,000 years.

36:10.280 --> 36:12.030
That's long enough.

36:12.060 --> 36:14.220
Chong Zhao has looked up to you as a father since he was a child,

36:14.250 --> 36:15.770
revering and admiring you.

36:15.790 --> 36:17.620
Yet you deceived him, betrayed him,

36:17.650 --> 36:19.380
and made him mistake a foe for family for so many years.

36:19.620 --> 36:20.500
Jin Yao,

36:20.890 --> 36:23.690
you claim to uphold the duty of protecting all beings

36:23.710 --> 36:25.350
and honor the responsibilities of the Eternals.

36:25.440 --> 36:27.950
But in the shadows, you've slaughtered your own kind for selfish gain!

36:34.260 --> 36:35.260
Bai Shuo,

36:36.090 --> 36:37.630
think back to

36:38.080 --> 36:39.850
when you were weak

36:39.870 --> 36:41.580
and had to watch helplessly

36:41.610 --> 36:44.150
as Cold Spring Palace wreaked havoc on Ning'an City.

36:45.060 --> 36:46.670
That feeling of powerlessness—

36:47.400 --> 36:48.970
I've felt it too.

36:49.000 --> 36:51.100
I once had a righteous heart.

36:51.410 --> 36:53.340
But back then, in Lanling,

36:53.370 --> 36:54.720
hierarchy was strict;

36:54.750 --> 36:55.790
status was clearly defined.

36:55.810 --> 36:57.290
I couldn't change it.

36:57.570 --> 37:00.050
When the Demon Race invaded, killing at will,

37:00.070 --> 37:01.840
I couldn't stop it either.

37:02.580 --> 37:03.890
The only way out

37:05.150 --> 37:06.840
was to become stronger.

37:07.470 --> 37:09.780
Only by becoming stronger could I do what I wanted to do

37:09.810 --> 37:11.480
and protect who I wanted to protect.

37:11.690 --> 37:13.950
But in the process of becoming stronger,

37:13.970 --> 37:15.310
my heart

37:15.540 --> 37:16.940
has changed.

37:17.630 --> 37:19.520
That's something you'll never understand.

37:20.360 --> 37:21.680
Today, Lanling is the head

37:22.470 --> 37:24.440
of all Eternal Sects.

37:25.030 --> 37:26.110
To its disciples,

37:26.130 --> 37:28.490
there is no longer oppression of rank or status.

37:28.520 --> 37:29.210
To outsiders,

37:29.230 --> 37:31.580
it's impenetrable, unmatched by any.

37:31.630 --> 37:34.140
Isn't that all thanks to me?

37:34.170 --> 37:35.160
Did I do wrong?

37:35.190 --> 37:36.360
You did.

37:38.280 --> 37:39.880
True strength

37:39.960 --> 37:41.660
should come from one's own efforts,

37:41.680 --> 37:43.280
not from achieving selfish goals

37:43.310 --> 37:44.710
at the cost of countless lives.

37:46.400 --> 37:48.360
Today, we'll seek justice for Chong Zhao's parents,

37:48.390 --> 37:49.450
for my master,

37:49.480 --> 37:52.540
and for the countless innocent souls in Bodhi Village.

37:53.060 --> 37:54.310
Justice

37:54.340 --> 37:56.730
has never been in words.

37:58.470 --> 37:59.870
It lies only

37:59.890 --> 38:01.670
in power.

38:17.370 --> 38:19.360
How do you possess such strong spiritual power?

38:19.720 --> 38:22.630
Did you really think the head of the Eternals

38:22.820 --> 38:24.970
was only capable of this much?

38:27.240 --> 38:29.800
During all these years of working with Luan Zhu,

38:29.840 --> 38:32.740
I've learned many ancient mental cultivation methods of the Divine Race.

38:33.160 --> 38:34.510
A century of cultivation

38:34.530 --> 38:36.140
has made me who I am today.

38:36.630 --> 38:38.900
Hiding my spiritual power

38:39.820 --> 38:42.360
has been quite exhausting.

38:42.580 --> 38:44.150
If you had such power,

38:44.400 --> 38:46.810
why did you let me steal the Contemplation Stone back then?

38:46.840 --> 38:48.680
As expected of the Master of Bright Moon,

38:48.700 --> 38:51.570
you hit the nail on the head.

38:52.130 --> 38:53.970
All these years, I couldn't figure out

38:54.000 --> 38:56.230
how to activate the Contemplation Stone.

38:56.410 --> 38:58.580
So I decided to play along,

38:58.610 --> 39:01.170
deliberately letting you steal the Contemplation Stone.

39:01.190 --> 39:03.310
I planned to wait until you gathered all Five Contemplations

39:03.340 --> 39:05.020
before taking it back.

39:05.400 --> 39:07.170
I didn't expect you to find Bai Shuo

39:07.230 --> 39:10.540
who was capable of activating the Contemplation Stone so quickly.

39:11.220 --> 39:12.900
But now, it seems

39:12.930 --> 39:15.080
you'll never gather all the Contemplations.

39:15.480 --> 39:16.880
Then,

39:16.910 --> 39:18.570
return the Contemplation Stone

39:19.410 --> 39:21.220
to me.

39:32.480 --> 39:34.960
I underestimated you.

39:34.980 --> 39:36.440
Take Bai Shuo and leave.

39:59.010 --> 40:00.030
Don't burn the star!

40:03.730 --> 40:04.930
Burn the star?

40:05.060 --> 40:07.500
My dear disciple Chong Zhao

40:07.530 --> 40:09.390
told me about the Seal

40:09.490 --> 40:12.090
in a letter a long time ago.

40:12.120 --> 40:14.370
Do you think I wouldn't be prepared?

40:14.390 --> 40:16.060
Chong Zhao trusted you so deeply,

40:16.080 --> 40:17.520
yet you only used him.

40:17.550 --> 40:18.750
How despicable!

40:19.540 --> 40:21.580
Luan Zhu once told me

40:21.600 --> 40:25.120
that the Seven-Star Seal comes from practicing ancient demonic techniques.

40:25.180 --> 40:26.630
And my spiritual power

40:26.650 --> 40:29.240
comes from the ancient Heart Sutra.

40:29.400 --> 40:30.520
Well, then,

40:30.540 --> 40:32.340
let's see

40:32.460 --> 40:36.070
if I can burn the last star of yours.

40:39.190 --> 40:40.220
No!

40:46.160 --> 40:47.680
From this moment on,

40:47.710 --> 40:50.750
the Master of Bright Moon no longer exists in this world.

40:59.700 --> 41:00.540
Fan Yue!

41:00.560 --> 41:01.450
Fan Yue!

41:02.870 --> 41:05.840
♫A lifetime of guarding everything with you♫

41:06.060 --> 41:09.530
♫Crossing the abyss to fulfill our vow♫

41:09.770 --> 41:13.180
♫I'll leap without a thought for tomorrow♫

41:13.610 --> 41:16.220
♫This moment feels like forever♫

41:16.440 --> 41:19.310
♫I've missed too much time in my life♫

41:19.620 --> 41:23.430
♫I'll throw myself into this flame for you♫

41:23.630 --> 41:25.620
♫Even if I'll perish♫

41:25.670 --> 41:28.400
♫At least I can still kiss your face♫

41:28.670 --> 41:32.390
♫Burn out my waning moon♫

41:31.600 --> 41:34.340
It's your turn now.

41:32.690 --> 41:41.110
♫In exchange for a lifetime of passion♫

41:35.600 --> 41:37.150
-No!
-Jin Yao!

42:18.650 --> 42:20.010
The Hidden power?

42:22.490 --> 42:25.370
You can actually control the Hidden power?

42:25.390 --> 42:27.090
Who exactly are you?

43:03.320 --> 43:04.030
Chong Zhao.

43:04.640 --> 43:05.300
Chong Zhao!

43:33.820 --> 43:34.900
Fan Yue.

43:35.990 --> 43:36.910
Fan Yue.

43:39.600 --> 43:40.560
Fan Yue!

43:41.230 --> 43:42.190
Fan Yue!
